                        </p><p>Rough nastaʿlīq in a relatively modern hand. 
</p><p>Reddish brown leather binding with brown leather edging, damaged; labels. 
</p><p>Folios mostly bound. 
</p><p>Previous owner’s inscription at beginning. 
